  "body": "<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/boUavhPr/images/59ff2b0a91fb5abe2a66b6434596ce7e2ec3bbad.png\" alt=\"Banner\">\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/793/502/_x__xampp_htdocs_mrcrayfish.png\">\n</p>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n    <h3>📖About:</h3>\n    <p>\n        Mod <span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong>Mr</strong></span><strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">Crayfish's Furniture Tools: Legacy</span></strong> \n        adds 3 new items for working with blocks from mod \n        <span style=\"color: #3598db;\">\n            <strong>\n                <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/mrcrayfish-furniture-mod\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">\n                    MrCrayfish's Furniture Mod: Legacy\n                </a>!\n            </strong>\n        </span>\n    </p>\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\nThis mod will be useful for those who love to build!\n</div>\n\n---\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n    <h3>🛠️Tools:</h3>\n    <p><span style=\"color: #fbeeb8;\"><strong>Rotation Tool - \nRotates the blocks</strong></span></p>\n    <p><span style=\"color: #f8cac6;\"><strong>Break Tool - Instantly breaks blocks</strong></span></p>\n    <p><span style=\"color: #c2e0f4;\"><strong>Multi Tool - \nBreak + Rotation</strong></span></p>\n</div>\n\n---\n\n<div align=\"center\"> \n<h3>⚙️Example of how the tools work</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MrPup-minecraftkus/MrCrayfishs-Furniture-Mod-Tools-Refurbished/refs/heads/test/1214.gif\" alt=\"tools\">\n</p>",
